					class="fas fa-mouse"></i>
				<li><a href="#" class="height-100p flex flex-ai-c has-list">SNS</a>
					<ul class="snsList">
						<li><a href="https://github.com/cyj420" target="blank">GITHUB</a>
							<i class="fas fa-mouse"></i>
